      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·010.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">載驅.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>載驅薄薄，簟茀朱鞹。魯道有蕩，齊子發夕。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>She urges on her chariot rapidly,
With its screen of bamboos woven in squares, and its vermilion-
coloured leather.
The way from Loo is easy and plain,
And the daughter of Ts'e started on it in the evening.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-qifeng-010__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
