      <prop type="x-translation-ref">載驅.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>四驪濟濟，垂轡濔濔。魯道有蕩，齊子豈弟。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Her four black horses are beautiful,
And soft look the reins as they hang.
The way from Loo is easy and plain,
And the daughter of Tsce is delighted and complacent.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
