      <prop type="x-translation-ref">載驅.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>汶水湯湯，行人彭彭。魯道有蕩，齊子翱翔。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The waters of the Wan flow broadly on;
The travellers are numerous.
The way from Loo is easy and plain,
And the daughter of Ts4e moves on with unconcern.</seg>
      </tuv>
