        <seg>汶水滔滔，行人儦儦。魯道有蕩，齊子遊敖。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The waters of the Wan sweep on;
The travellers are in crowds.
The way from Loo is easy and plain,
